      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-4">Our Accommodation</fullscreen-image.pngh2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] max-w-2xl mx-auto">Clarence's Cattery was designed purely for the comfort, happiness and safety of each guest. Built by my husband David (AKA Uncle Dave) and purchased from Pedigree Pens, every detail has been thought through with cats in mind.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>

      <!-- Cattery overview -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-4">A Home in Our Garden</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] leading-relaxed">
            <p>The cattery is completely UPVC which is absolutely fantastic as a high level of cleanliness can be kept at all times. The roof is made from a heat reflective material which keeps it cool in the summer, and each bedroom is fitted with a thermostatically controlled heater for the colder days.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>It sits in our garden, very close to our home, so even when we are not in there (which is hardly ever) we can see in and the cats can see us.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>There are strictly no communal areas. Pussycats from different households are not allowed to mix, to ensure everyone is safe, healthy and happy. The mesh in the top of the safety corridor allows a constant flow of fresh air for guests to breathe in.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>Classic FM is always playing in the corridor as a firm favourite, rather than Auntie's singing!</fullscreen-image.pngp>
          </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <img
            src="/fullscreen-image.pngP9488/fullscreen-image.pngimages/fullscreen-image.pngcopy-of-review-aaagain-10-x-40-in-3-1.jpg"
            alt="Clarence's Cattery accommodation"
            width="800" height="600"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          /fullscreen-image.png>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>

      <!-- Six suites grid -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-center mb-8">Our Six Named Suites</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">Each suite has a bedroom with an iron bed for loungers and a pod for those who like to curl up, all furnished with fluffy blankets. There is also a second room with a tower, scratching posts, hidey hole, a small chair for fluffy bottoms and a selection of toys. Very high shelves too, for the adventurous climbers!</fullscreen-image.pngp>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-md group">
          <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/fullscreen-image.pngP9488/fullscreen-image.pngimages/fullscreen-image.pngimg-20250804-wa0001.jpg" alt="Frog Suite" width="500" height="500" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" /fullscreen-image.png>
