        Each suite can accommodate two pussycats from the same household. For families of more than two, the suites can be opened up with the suite next door. The front of each suite is pawsafe mesh which leads to a safety corridor looking out onto our garden.
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
    </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
  </fullscreen-image.pngsection>

  <!-- What makes us different -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[var(--color-ink)] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center mb-10">What Makes Clarence's Different?</fullscreen-image.pngh2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white/fullscreen-image.png10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌙</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] mb-2">Around the Clock</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
          <p class="text-white/fullscreen-image.png80 text-sm">Kerry is here all the time and can adapt her day to suit the guests. If there is a thunderstorm in the middle of the night, she will get up and check on every baby.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        <div class="bg-white/fullscreen-image.png10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🧽</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] mb-2">Spotlessly Clean</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
          <p class="text-white/fullscreen-image.png80 text-sm">The full UPVC construction means an extremely high level of cleanliness can be kept at all times. All DEFRA regulations are consistently adhered to.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        <div class="bg-white/fullscreen-image.png10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💛</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] mb-2">Individual Care</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
          <p class="text-white/fullscreen-image.png80 text-sm">Hand feeding, tummy tickles, teeth cleaning, five meals a day, snuggles on demand. Whatever your pussycat needs to make their holiday a contented, memorable one.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white/fullscreen-image.png10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-white/fullscreen-image.png90 leading-relaxed">The garden is full of plant pots which attract butterflies and bees for the pussycats to watch. We even get a cheeky squirrel called Steve who makes many an appearance to keep them entertained, and a heron who loves to land with his big feet on the roof!</fullscreen-image.pngp>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
    </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
  </fullscreen-image.pngsection>

  <!-- Prices -->
  <section id="prices" class="py-20 bg-[var(--color-cream)]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-4">Prices</fullscreen-image.pngh2>
