          <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] mb-2">£26</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <div class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">per day</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <div class="text-white/fullscreen-image.png70 text-sm">for two pussycats sharing one suite</fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>

      <!-- What's included -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-4">All prices include food, litter and treats</fullscreen-image.pngh3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-2">Wet Food</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm">Felix AGAIL, Sheba, Purina Gourmet and Whiskas.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-2 mt-4">Dry Food</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm">Royal Canin Sensible, Purina One and Iams.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
          </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-2">Treats</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm">Webbox Licky Lix, meat sticks, Dreamies, Felix Goody Bags and freeze-dried. We also always have tinned tuna, fresh tuna, chicken and Kerry's famous Tuna Surprise to entice our fussier guests.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
          </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        <p class="mt-6 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm border-t border-[var(--color-border)] pt-4">If you would like your baby to stay on a particular diet, you are welcome to bring their own food. Please ensure you provide enough for their entire stay.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>

      <!-- Prices also include -->
      <div class="bg-[var(--color-accent-light)] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-semibold mb-2">Prices also include Kerry.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm">Lots of playtime and as many snuggles as they would like. Time is taken to get to know each pussycat and their individual personality. We also provide photo and video updates on our Facebook page or directly by WhatsApp so you can see what we get up to!</fullscreen-image.pngp>
      </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>

