    </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
  </fullscreen-image.pngsection>

  <!-- About /fullscreen-image.png Story -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-[var(--color-brand-bg)]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">

      <!-- What's in a Name -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-20">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-6">What's in a Name?</fullscreen-image.pngh2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] leading-relaxed">
            <p>Our cattery is named after our handsome, gentle, caring boy Clarence. We sadly lost him in June 2016 at the very grand age of 24 years old. Kerry was privileged to have had Clarence with her since he was 9 weeks old, rescued from a farm where he was neglected and mistreated.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>As a kitten, he was extremely mischievous: climbing curtains, sitting on rooftops, fighting with Kerry's pigtails and even stealing a joint of beef from the next door neighbour's kitchen worktop!</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>In his older years, he was a best friend to both of Kerry's children. They dressed him up, put make-up on him, talked to him, and most importantly, they loved him to pieces.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
            <p>Clarence was so loving, so affectionate, and his love unconditional. We all miss him terribly but were honoured to have him in our lives.</fullscreen-image.pngp>
          </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        </fullscreen-image.pngdiv>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
